title: (4aS, 5S, 6aR, 10aR, 10bR)-5-Methoxy-9,9-Dimethyl-4a, 5,6a, 7,10a, 10b-Hexahydro-12H-[1,3]dioxino[4′, 5’:5,6]pyrano[4,3-b][1,2, 3]triazolo[1,5-d][1,4]oxazine
content: A new tetracyclic morpholine-fused [5,1-c]-triazole, (4aS,5S,6aR,10aR,10bR)-5-methoxy-9,9-dimethyl-4a,5,6a,7,10a,10b-hexahydro-12H-[1,3]dioxino[4',5':5,6]pyrano[4,3-b][1,2,3]triazolo[1,5-d][1,4]oxazine, was synthesized via a five-step sequence starting from methyl Î±-D-glucopyranoside by using as a key step an intramolecular copper(I) cat-alyzed alkyne-azide cycloaddition (CuAAC). The synthesized compound was fully characterized by 1H and 13C NMR, FT-IR, and HRMS.
